channel.title: NanoLinks News
channel.description: Great news easily gets buried in a continuous media stream like Reddit and Discord. Here we try to keep track of the most important Nano news.

item.title: The Nano Center Google Ads Project Funded & Live!
item.description: Another amazing project funded at The Nano Center https://nanocenter.org/projects/google-ads-display Campaign is underway now! Thanks to all who donated. Results of the campaign will be presented by /u/kojoslayer throughout the project and after completion.
